Website blocking
Navigate to:
https://security.microsoft.com/preferences2/custom_ti_indicators~2Furl?tid=f535743e-b6ee-4533-8cf5-b1e76dd9ae2b
Under "Rules" go to "Indicators"
Choose IP addresses or URLs/Domains
Click "Add Item"
Enter the IP address or URL
Go through the menu choosing the options you want
Done

File Blocking:
Navigate to:
https://security.microsoft.com/preferences2/custom_ti_indicators~2Furl?tid=f535743e-b6ee-4533-8cf5-b1e76dd9ae2b
Under "Rules" go to "Indicators"
Choose File Hash
Click "Add Item"
Enter File Hash
Go through the menu choosing the options you want
Done
